WEBVTT

00:01:08.425 --> 00:01:10.225
We were just two girls
finding out who we really were

00:01:10.305 --> 00:01:12.105
and happened to cross paths. Nothing more.

00:01:12.185 --> 00:01:13.465
And what about now?

00:01:14.065 --> 00:01:16.145
Now I've found the one I love the most.

00:01:16.225 --> 00:01:18.625
We decided to postpone Play Park's closure

00:01:18.705 --> 00:01:20.185
indefinitely.

00:01:20.265 --> 00:01:22.305
-Yeah!
-Yay!

00:01:22.385 --> 00:01:23.745
Manager.

00:01:25.465 --> 00:01:26.985
I've told you before

00:01:27.065 --> 00:01:30.265
that I don't care who you're close with.

00:01:30.345 --> 00:01:32.145
But if whoever or whatever

00:01:32.225 --> 00:01:35.425
stands in the way
of the life goal I've set for you,

00:01:36.025 --> 00:01:37.425
I wouldn't let it go.

00:01:58.385 --> 00:01:59.585
I'm sorry.

00:02:00.825 --> 00:02:02.225
I shouldn't have--

00:05:09.225 --> 00:05:11.105
You went abroad for a meeting

00:05:12.305 --> 00:05:14.905
and didn't answer my calls.
That, I can understand.

00:05:16.065 --> 00:05:17.985
But you left without even telling me.

00:05:18.625 --> 00:05:21.065
You even left my texts on read.

00:05:21.585 --> 00:05:22.985
What was that supposed to mean?

00:05:25.865 --> 00:05:28.105
I wanted to try fading away for a while.

00:05:28.665 --> 00:05:29.865
Ms. Lin.

00:05:31.105 --> 00:05:33.825
I thought it might end quietly,

00:05:34.345 --> 00:05:36.305
but it didn't.

00:05:38.265 --> 00:05:40.225
But why did it have to end?

00:05:42.025 --> 00:05:43.225
Was it because

00:05:44.065 --> 00:05:46.185
your father didn't want us to be together?

00:05:52.945 --> 00:05:56.385
Jane said your father is very concerned
about the company’s work.

00:05:57.425 --> 00:05:58.905
Was it because of that?

00:06:02.345 --> 00:06:04.265
You need to separate the issues.

00:06:04.345 --> 00:06:06.265
It’s not that
Dad doesn’t like you personally,

00:06:06.985 --> 00:06:10.505
he doesn't like anyone
who causes setbacks in my work.

00:06:12.145 --> 00:06:14.625
He has high expectations for me.

00:06:16.865 --> 00:06:19.265
So you chose to leave me

00:06:20.905 --> 00:06:23.225
instead of working it out together?

00:06:29.905 --> 00:06:31.425
Listen to me, okay?

00:06:33.185 --> 00:06:35.505
I was so worried, you know?

00:06:36.105 --> 00:06:39.065
I was afraid
you would get in trouble for dating me.

00:06:42.145 --> 00:06:44.545
And don't you think
me being unable to eat or sleep

00:06:45.985 --> 00:06:47.665
was trouble enough?

00:06:49.665 --> 00:06:51.065
I'm sorry.

00:06:53.265 --> 00:06:56.625
I needed to take a step back
to avoid conflict with Dad.

00:06:57.945 --> 00:07:01.865
I had to stop everything
before our relationship got worse.

00:07:04.465 --> 00:07:07.625
I was afraid it would end up
like what happened with Prae.

00:07:13.665 --> 00:07:16.265
So I needed some time alone

00:07:16.865 --> 00:07:19.545
to process everything.

00:07:21.385 --> 00:07:22.865
Once I figured it out,

00:07:22.945 --> 00:07:25.425
I rushed back to you.

00:07:32.985 --> 00:07:35.265
If we can prove to Dad

00:07:35.345 --> 00:07:38.225
that our relationship helps us
support each other's careers,

00:07:39.785 --> 00:07:42.505
maybe he won't stand in our way.

00:07:48.865 --> 00:07:50.625
I know it's not easy.

00:07:51.225 --> 00:07:52.825
We still have a lot to fight for.

00:07:55.305 --> 00:07:57.105
Will you fight alongside me?

00:08:00.505 --> 00:08:02.905
I just happen to be
a fighter who doesn’t back down.

00:08:07.865 --> 00:08:10.385
Please don't walk away from me again.

00:08:12.985 --> 00:08:14.345
If there's a next time,

00:08:14.865 --> 00:08:16.865
I'll let you walk alone.

00:08:19.625 --> 00:08:20.905
I've learned my lesson.

00:08:38.985 --> 00:08:41.065
So that's why she turned off her phone.

00:08:46.225 --> 00:08:47.345
Are you asleep, Gib?

00:08:48.345 --> 00:08:50.865
Sorry. Can I ask you something?

00:08:50.945 --> 00:08:53.265
Did anyone go to see Ms. Lin
at the house today?

00:09:00.425 --> 00:09:01.425
Mm.

00:09:15.305 --> 00:09:17.665
Ms. Lin, please be honest.

00:09:18.465 --> 00:09:21.785
Did you put off
Play Park's closing date indefinitely

00:09:23.185 --> 00:09:24.545
because of me?

00:09:29.185 --> 00:09:31.025
I feel really bad

00:09:33.505 --> 00:09:35.625
for causing trouble
between you and your father.

00:09:37.345 --> 00:09:39.065
Don't blame yourself.

00:09:40.305 --> 00:09:42.905
I didn't do it to please you.

00:09:44.985 --> 00:09:47.665
But I really agree with your idea.

00:09:51.465 --> 00:09:52.745
What idea?

00:09:56.825 --> 00:09:58.105
I understand now

00:09:58.745 --> 00:10:01.105
why you want to open a tutoring school.

00:10:02.185 --> 00:10:05.305
It’s because
you attended those schools yourself

00:10:05.385 --> 00:10:07.425
and became successful.

00:10:09.385 --> 00:10:10.905
You don't agree with the method?

00:10:12.505 --> 00:10:14.545
It's not that I don't agree with it.

00:10:15.345 --> 00:10:16.505
But…

00:10:17.025 --> 00:10:19.465
I think if kids really have to study,

00:10:19.545 --> 00:10:21.145
they should be playing too.

00:10:21.225 --> 00:10:24.665
It allows them
to grow and learn at the same time.

00:10:24.745 --> 00:10:26.785
It's better than attending
tutoring school every day.

00:10:26.865 --> 00:10:28.585
They’d be so stressed.

00:10:45.385 --> 00:10:46.905
I wasn't even being serious.

00:10:46.985 --> 00:10:49.385
I didn't expect you
to think so much about it.

00:10:52.705 --> 00:10:55.545
It hit so close to home.
How could I not think about it?

00:10:57.065 --> 00:11:00.625
I did try to capitalize
on what parents need.

00:11:02.705 --> 00:11:04.705
I feel like a terrible person.

00:11:08.625 --> 00:11:10.985
You're running a business.
Of course you look for profit.

00:11:11.665 --> 00:11:12.945
Also,

00:11:13.505 --> 00:11:14.985
you’re not just running

00:11:15.065 --> 00:11:16.825
this tutoring school.

00:11:19.425 --> 00:11:21.505
You're good at comforting people, huh?

00:11:25.505 --> 00:11:26.865
I need to find a way

00:11:26.945 --> 00:11:29.745
to make the business model more seamless.

00:11:33.225 --> 00:11:35.545
Tell me if you need any help.

00:11:37.905 --> 00:11:41.945
Just staying by my side like this
and not going anywhere is enough.

00:13:07.185 --> 00:13:09.065
Lin. Lin.

00:13:14.065 --> 00:13:14.905
Dad.

00:13:18.625 --> 00:13:19.825
How was the meeting?

00:13:20.505 --> 00:13:22.745
Let's talk about it at your house later.

00:13:24.625 --> 00:13:26.185
IngIng, come on out.

00:13:53.545 --> 00:13:54.705
Hello.

00:14:13.305 --> 00:14:14.225
Dad.

00:14:14.745 --> 00:14:16.945
I've found my baking instructor.

00:14:33.145 --> 00:14:35.745
IngIng is the manager at Play Park.

00:14:37.825 --> 00:14:39.145
So if Play Park shuts down,

00:14:39.225 --> 00:14:40.425
would you be out of work?

00:14:40.945 --> 00:14:42.385
No, sir.

00:14:42.465 --> 00:14:44.625
Mr. Pao has already found me another job.

00:14:46.145 --> 00:14:49.345
Play Park's customers love her
and trust her very much, Dad.

00:14:49.425 --> 00:14:52.225
If we get her to help us with PR,
it’ll be easier

00:14:52.305 --> 00:14:54.625
for customers to apply for our courses.

00:14:58.785 --> 00:15:01.785
I’ll help Ms. Lin the best I can.

00:15:05.545 --> 00:15:07.545
You did what I asked

00:15:07.625 --> 00:15:09.865
to buy yourself some time, didn't you?

00:15:12.745 --> 00:15:15.385
Anyway, don't let the construction
be delayed for too long,

00:15:15.465 --> 00:15:17.985
because the board
is watching your progress.

00:15:18.865 --> 00:15:20.065
Yes, Dad.

00:15:23.425 --> 00:15:26.425
Then let’s talk more at my house later.

00:15:27.945 --> 00:15:29.385
I’ll walk you out.

00:15:29.465 --> 00:15:31.545
It's okay. Stay with your friend.

00:15:53.305 --> 00:15:54.385
Let's eat.

00:15:54.465 --> 00:15:55.745
I've already cooked for you.

00:15:55.825 --> 00:15:56.745
Let's go.

00:16:03.185 --> 00:16:04.465
CHANNEL 3 NEWS FAMILY

00:16:09.305 --> 00:16:12.145
Manager, have you ever seen
the fugitive before?

00:16:12.225 --> 00:16:13.265
I haven’t.

00:16:13.345 --> 00:16:16.145
And no one on the staff knows him either.

00:16:16.225 --> 00:16:17.385
Other than you,

00:16:17.465 --> 00:16:19.785
was anyone injured?

00:16:19.865 --> 00:16:20.985
No.

00:16:21.065 --> 00:16:23.745
Luckily, Play Park
wasn't open yet at that hour,

00:16:23.825 --> 00:16:25.705
so there were no customers inside.

00:16:25.785 --> 00:16:27.945
That was fortunate.

00:16:28.025 --> 00:16:29.865
Yes, we were very lucky.

00:17:37.465 --> 00:17:38.585
May.

00:17:38.665 --> 00:17:39.905
RECHARGE STATION

00:17:39.985 --> 00:17:41.265
Come on, come on.

00:17:49.665 --> 00:17:51.505
Okay, lift the left side a little.

00:17:53.065 --> 00:17:54.145
That's it. Lock it in place.

00:17:54.225 --> 00:17:56.145
I’ll go ahead and secure it, alright?

00:17:59.345 --> 00:18:00.185
Beautiful.

00:18:00.265 --> 00:18:02.065
Perfect. Yay!

00:18:02.145 --> 00:18:03.985
-Yeah!
-Yay!

00:18:04.065 --> 00:18:05.425
So beautiful.

00:18:05.505 --> 00:18:07.625
Everyone, let's take group photos.

00:18:09.505 --> 00:18:11.585
-Yay!
-Yay!

00:18:22.665 --> 00:18:24.185
So great.

00:18:24.705 --> 00:18:26.305
Great job, guys.

00:18:26.385 --> 00:18:28.665
-Fabulous.
-Well done.

00:18:35.345 --> 00:18:36.945
Are you done?

00:18:37.025 --> 00:18:38.425
Is it too late to change my mind?

00:18:39.025 --> 00:18:40.705
Oh? Why are you changing your mind?

00:18:40.785 --> 00:18:42.905
It doesn't really suit me.

00:18:42.985 --> 00:18:45.665
Come out and I’ll tell you
whether it suits you or not.

00:18:46.265 --> 00:18:47.305
Don't laugh, okay?

00:18:48.105 --> 00:18:49.185
Mm.

00:18:49.265 --> 00:18:50.745
I'm covering my mouth.

00:19:05.265 --> 00:19:06.825
You look cute.

00:19:06.905 --> 00:19:08.465
Don't I look funny?

00:19:08.545 --> 00:19:09.425
Not at all.

00:19:09.505 --> 00:19:11.465
Kids love costumes like this.

00:19:12.065 --> 00:19:14.425
-I’m not doing it.
-No.

00:19:14.945 --> 00:19:16.065
It was your idea.

00:19:16.145 --> 00:19:17.665
You have to wear it. Let's go.

00:19:21.225 --> 00:19:22.945
-What's this?
-I'm calculating.

00:19:23.025 --> 00:19:24.505
-Calculating right now.
-Really?

00:19:24.585 --> 00:19:26.385
Welcome. Right this way.

00:19:26.465 --> 00:19:27.785
So what is it?

00:19:27.865 --> 00:19:29.105
What's the number?

00:19:29.185 --> 00:19:30.025
Huh?

00:19:30.105 --> 00:19:32.585
What's the number? No.

00:19:32.665 --> 00:19:34.625
I don't have enough fingers to count.

00:19:34.705 --> 00:19:35.585
Fingers?

00:19:35.665 --> 00:19:36.945
Then can you start from nine?

00:19:37.025 --> 00:19:38.425
Nine, ten,

00:19:38.505 --> 00:19:39.345
eleven,

00:19:39.425 --> 00:19:40.585
-twelve.
-Nine, ten.

00:19:40.665 --> 00:19:41.865
Eleven, twelve.

00:19:41.945 --> 00:19:43.105
-What is this?
-Thirteen.

00:19:45.385 --> 00:19:46.865
-You're so cool.
-Nine.

00:19:46.945 --> 00:19:48.425
Hi.

00:19:48.505 --> 00:19:49.745
Hi. Thank you.

00:19:49.825 --> 00:19:51.305
Thank you.

00:19:51.385 --> 00:19:52.705
Okay, okay.

00:19:54.665 --> 00:19:57.145
-Here you go.
-Are you doing it again?

00:20:03.305 --> 00:20:04.225
Is that right?

00:20:05.785 --> 00:20:08.145
What about the other one?

00:20:08.225 --> 00:20:09.745
The one on the left.

00:20:09.825 --> 00:20:11.305
On the left?

00:20:11.385 --> 00:20:13.145
-It's six.
-Oh, six?

00:20:13.865 --> 00:20:15.785
This one? Yeah.

00:20:15.865 --> 00:20:17.945
-Is that it?
-Is it right?

00:20:27.185 --> 00:20:29.465
A lot of parents
are interested in our booth.

00:20:29.545 --> 00:20:30.785
Really?

00:20:31.305 --> 00:20:33.345
The kids were having a lot of fun too.

00:20:33.425 --> 00:20:35.865
You're good. You've got the right idea.

00:20:36.665 --> 00:20:40.265
But the kids looked so happy.
They were all busy solving math problems.

00:20:40.785 --> 00:20:43.585
Some even came back to ask for the answers
and challenge each other.

00:20:43.665 --> 00:20:46.065
-Yeah?
-They enjoyed it so much.

00:20:46.145 --> 00:20:47.345
That's funny.

00:20:49.225 --> 00:20:52.385
Then can I get my commission upfront?

00:20:54.985 --> 00:20:56.625
How about a trip to Pattaya instead?

00:20:56.705 --> 00:20:58.225
I have a seminar there soon.

00:20:58.825 --> 00:21:00.025
Let me think about it.

00:21:02.985 --> 00:21:03.905
Please?

00:21:04.705 --> 00:21:05.545
Okay?

00:21:12.585 --> 00:21:13.465
Mm.

00:21:23.585 --> 00:21:25.465
It's him! It's him!

00:21:25.545 --> 00:21:26.705
Sir.

00:21:27.385 --> 00:21:30.025
This lady told me
you were stalking her boss.

00:21:30.105 --> 00:21:31.985
This is a misunderstanding.

00:21:32.065 --> 00:21:33.505
I don't even know her boss.

00:21:35.465 --> 00:21:37.265
Then show us what’s on your phone.

00:21:37.345 --> 00:21:38.865
I saw you filming my boss.

00:21:38.945 --> 00:21:40.425
What? Who are you?

00:21:40.505 --> 00:21:42.425
-What do you want from me?
-And who are you?

00:21:44.625 --> 00:21:46.025
I'm her ex-husband.

00:21:46.105 --> 00:21:48.305
Are you crazy?
My boss has never been married.

00:21:48.385 --> 00:21:50.225
Is IngIng your boss?

00:21:51.905 --> 00:21:52.905
Huh?

00:21:56.225 --> 00:21:57.945
You're IngIng's husband?

00:21:58.025 --> 00:21:58.985
Yeah.

00:22:05.305 --> 00:22:07.505
DROP-OFF POINT

00:22:17.345 --> 00:22:18.665
See you.

00:22:18.745 --> 00:22:19.785
Bye-bye.

00:22:22.105 --> 00:22:24.025
Ms. Lin, why didn't you wait for me?

00:22:24.105 --> 00:22:24.945
Let’s go.

00:22:25.025 --> 00:22:26.785
Uncle Somchai, open the door.

00:22:26.865 --> 00:22:28.025
-Let's go.
-What’s going on?

00:22:28.105 --> 00:22:29.465
Let's leave. It's not safe here.

00:22:30.305 --> 00:22:31.665
See you, Ing.

00:22:33.625 --> 00:22:34.705
Let's go.

00:22:44.545 --> 00:22:45.905
Let's get moving.

00:23:16.305 --> 00:23:17.865
Tickle, tickle.

00:23:17.945 --> 00:23:19.945
It tickles, right?

00:23:20.025 --> 00:23:20.985
Here.

00:23:21.065 --> 00:23:23.025
Whose crocodile is this?

00:23:23.785 --> 00:23:26.665
Oh, it’s a seal. Whose seal is this?

00:23:29.785 --> 00:23:31.025
-Whoa.
-Wow.

00:23:33.705 --> 00:23:35.945
-Take a photo of us, Ith.
-Alright.

00:23:36.545 --> 00:23:38.665
Look at the camera, Donut.

00:23:38.745 --> 00:23:40.825
-Look at the camera.
-One, two…

00:23:40.905 --> 00:23:41.905
Whoa.

00:23:41.985 --> 00:23:42.945
Donut. Donut.

00:23:45.105 --> 00:23:46.265
Yeah.

00:23:46.785 --> 00:23:47.825
One, two.

00:23:47.905 --> 00:23:49.305
-Does it look cute?
-So cute.

00:23:49.825 --> 00:23:51.105
I mean Donut is so cute.

00:23:51.185 --> 00:23:52.585
Yeah, I know.

00:23:53.225 --> 00:23:54.505
Come here.

00:23:56.385 --> 00:23:57.825
One, two, three.

00:23:57.905 --> 00:24:04.865
Three. Three. Three.

00:24:06.705 --> 00:24:07.945
Three.

00:24:08.025 --> 00:24:09.545
-Peekaboo!
-You want the seal?

00:24:09.625 --> 00:24:12.425
Whose son is this? So cute, right?

00:24:12.505 --> 00:24:13.745
Right?

00:24:13.825 --> 00:24:16.465
Okay, the seal's here.
You like the seal, right?

00:24:19.785 --> 00:24:21.345
Come on. One, two…

00:24:24.545 --> 00:24:25.705
-One, two, three.
-What is it?

00:24:28.145 --> 00:24:29.145
Three.

00:24:41.985 --> 00:24:44.025
Ith, take Donut.

00:24:47.505 --> 00:24:48.585
-Come here.
-Go to Uncle Ith.

00:24:48.665 --> 00:24:50.345
Sit here with me, okay?

00:25:00.545 --> 00:25:02.825
Stay with Uncle Ith, alright?
Stay with me.

00:25:06.225 --> 00:25:07.785
Long time no see.

00:25:08.545 --> 00:25:09.625
Why are you here?

00:25:10.465 --> 00:25:12.025
Well, I missed my child.

00:25:12.545 --> 00:25:13.465
I want to see his face.

00:25:15.905 --> 00:25:17.745
-Can I come inside?
-No.

00:25:18.585 --> 00:25:20.025
You're not welcome here.

00:25:21.025 --> 00:25:21.985
Why are you here?

00:25:22.505 --> 00:25:23.825
Donut.

00:25:23.905 --> 00:25:25.025
Wow.

00:25:25.105 --> 00:25:26.665
My son is this big now?

00:25:26.745 --> 00:25:27.785
Donut, come here.

00:25:28.425 --> 00:25:30.585
Let's go inside, okay?

00:25:34.265 --> 00:25:35.065
Get out.

00:25:37.305 --> 00:25:39.105
Before I call the police.

00:25:39.185 --> 00:25:40.785
Do I have to listen to you?

00:25:59.465 --> 00:26:01.145
Why are you only telling me this now?

00:26:02.305 --> 00:26:05.225
If I’d told you earlier,
you wouldn’t have wanted to come home.

00:26:05.305 --> 00:26:07.305
I still can't get over

00:26:07.385 --> 00:26:08.905
that fugitive pointing a gun at you.

00:26:08.985 --> 00:26:10.625
Your safety has to come first.

00:26:10.705 --> 00:26:13.465
And did he say why he was stalking IngIng?

00:26:14.585 --> 00:26:17.345
He only said he thought
she might be his ex-wife,

00:26:17.425 --> 00:26:19.305
so he came to see for himself.

00:26:19.385 --> 00:26:21.625
But I don't buy it, Ms. Lin.

00:26:21.705 --> 00:26:23.745
I think it's possible
they're still together

00:26:23.825 --> 00:26:25.145
and trying to trick you.

00:26:25.745 --> 00:26:28.465
That's impossible.
Ing would never lie to me.

00:26:28.545 --> 00:26:30.385
You never know, Ms. Lin.

00:26:30.465 --> 00:26:32.105
Appearances can be misleading.

00:26:32.185 --> 00:26:34.705
And the two of you
haven’t known each other

00:26:34.785 --> 00:26:36.065
that long, right?

00:26:54.585 --> 00:26:56.665
LILIN

00:27:12.425 --> 00:27:14.625
Donut, don’t be afraid, okay?

00:27:14.705 --> 00:27:16.065
No need to be scared.

00:27:16.585 --> 00:27:17.785
I'm right here.

00:27:17.865 --> 00:27:19.785
I'm right here, alright?

00:27:20.665 --> 00:27:21.865
IngIng.

00:27:25.905 --> 00:27:28.145
Where are you two hiding?

00:27:32.665 --> 00:27:34.505
Why are you scared of me?

00:27:34.585 --> 00:27:35.985
I just missed my son

00:27:36.065 --> 00:27:37.065
and wanted to see him.

00:27:38.585 --> 00:27:39.705
Come out.

00:27:39.785 --> 00:27:41.505
Let's talk nicely.

00:27:46.945 --> 00:27:48.185
IngIng.

00:27:48.705 --> 00:27:50.585
Are you playing hide-and-seek with me?

00:27:54.505 --> 00:27:55.545
Good.

00:27:56.265 --> 00:27:58.025
Then hide properly.

00:27:59.785 --> 00:28:01.705
Because Daddy’s coming to find you.

00:28:07.025 --> 00:28:07.905
LILIN
MISSED CALL

00:28:08.545 --> 00:28:09.905
Ing's not answering her phone.

00:28:10.585 --> 00:28:12.265
She might be taking care of her child.

00:28:14.185 --> 00:28:15.505
I have a bad feeling about this.

00:28:16.905 --> 00:28:18.385
Ms. Lin, where are you going?

00:28:18.465 --> 00:28:21.145
Ms. Lin, please wait for me.

00:28:24.905 --> 00:28:27.345
Are you in here?

00:28:29.105 --> 00:28:30.145
Aha!

00:28:33.305 --> 00:28:34.505
Not here.

00:28:40.505 --> 00:28:42.545
Or is it…

00:28:45.065 --> 00:28:46.105
this room?

00:28:53.745 --> 00:28:55.505
Not here either.

00:28:57.065 --> 00:28:58.825
So it must be…

00:29:06.985 --> 00:29:08.745
Find somewhere good to hide.

00:29:10.065 --> 00:29:12.265
Daddy's right at the door.

00:29:15.545 --> 00:29:16.985
Peekaboo!

00:29:28.905 --> 00:29:30.025
IngIng.

00:29:30.585 --> 00:29:32.025
Why are you hiding?

00:29:32.785 --> 00:29:33.945
Just come out and talk.

00:29:34.025 --> 00:29:36.145
I just missed him and wanted to see him.

00:29:43.825 --> 00:29:44.865
No need to be afraid.

00:29:44.945 --> 00:29:46.585
I won’t do anything to either of you.

00:29:54.905 --> 00:29:55.985
IngIng.

00:29:57.545 --> 00:29:58.825
IngIng, come out.

00:30:00.145 --> 00:30:03.345
-Don't be afraid.
-Open the door for me, IngIng.

00:30:05.585 --> 00:30:06.665
IngIng.

00:30:07.305 --> 00:30:08.665
Ing!

00:30:08.745 --> 00:30:10.105
I said come out!

00:30:18.705 --> 00:30:20.225
Let's talk out here.

00:30:21.145 --> 00:30:22.025
Okay?

00:30:25.625 --> 00:30:27.385
Or do I need to break in?

00:30:30.345 --> 00:30:32.425
IngIng, I'm calling your name
for the last time.

00:30:33.225 --> 00:30:34.905
If you still won't open the door,

00:30:34.985 --> 00:30:36.105
this is your last chance.

00:30:38.665 --> 00:30:39.905
IngIng!

00:30:39.985 --> 00:30:41.145
Damn it!

00:30:41.665 --> 00:30:42.745
Open the door!

00:30:43.585 --> 00:30:45.025
I said open the door!

00:30:49.345 --> 00:30:51.025
Ugh! Let go of me!

00:30:55.345 --> 00:30:56.305
IngIng.

00:31:03.265 --> 00:31:04.265
Come here.

00:31:04.785 --> 00:31:05.985
Where are you running to?

00:31:06.665 --> 00:31:08.785
We’re husband and wife.
Why can’t we sleep together?

00:31:08.865 --> 00:31:09.825
Huh?

00:31:10.505 --> 00:31:11.825
Do I have to transition
into a woman for you?

00:31:17.425 --> 00:31:19.185
-Ing.
-Don't come any closer.

00:31:19.265 --> 00:31:20.825
I'm your husband, IngIng.

00:31:21.585 --> 00:31:23.385
We're legally married.

00:31:25.105 --> 00:31:26.585
Why can't I sleep with you?

00:31:27.185 --> 00:31:28.305
But we agreed on this.

00:31:28.385 --> 00:31:30.225
I agreed to marry you

00:31:32.145 --> 00:31:33.465
because I love you.

00:31:36.265 --> 00:31:38.985
Wasn't it because
my dad agreed to write off your debt?

00:31:44.025 --> 00:31:44.985
Yeah.

00:31:45.985 --> 00:31:47.825
Who says a husband
can't force himself on his wife?

00:31:49.145 --> 00:31:50.225
Don’t come any closer.

00:31:50.945 --> 00:31:52.305
If you touch me,

00:31:52.385 --> 00:31:53.625
I'll report you the police.

00:31:55.345 --> 00:31:56.465
Report me?

00:31:58.065 --> 00:31:59.385
For what?

00:32:01.545 --> 00:32:03.065
Sexual assault.

00:32:05.585 --> 00:32:07.705
If you can’t handle it,
just get a divorce.

00:32:07.785 --> 00:32:09.345
What are you even saying?

00:32:11.585 --> 00:32:13.025
I won't divorce you.

00:32:23.425 --> 00:32:24.265
IngIng.

00:32:26.225 --> 00:32:27.185
IngIng.

00:32:27.705 --> 00:32:29.345
Let me come in and hold our son.

00:32:32.745 --> 00:32:33.785
IngIng.

00:32:35.105 --> 00:32:36.425
Please open the door for me.

00:32:36.505 --> 00:32:37.865
I promise

00:32:38.385 --> 00:32:39.625
I won't do anything to him.

00:32:41.305 --> 00:32:42.145
Please, IngIng.

00:32:43.785 --> 00:32:44.665
IngIng.

00:32:46.505 --> 00:32:48.345
IngIng, I'm his father too.

00:32:49.865 --> 00:32:51.185
Open the door for me.

00:32:55.265 --> 00:32:56.585
IngIng.

00:32:59.025 --> 00:32:59.945
IngIng.

00:33:01.025 --> 00:33:02.865
Can I hold our son?

00:33:05.825 --> 00:33:07.265
I'm sorry.

00:33:08.625 --> 00:33:11.865
I came here just to see our son, really.

00:33:12.505 --> 00:33:13.745
Please let me hold him.

00:33:17.545 --> 00:33:19.305
I won't do anything to him, IngIng.

00:33:21.105 --> 00:33:23.305
I'm his father too.

00:33:27.785 --> 00:33:28.625
Just think of it

00:33:29.585 --> 00:33:31.985
as me being his father for the last time.

00:33:32.985 --> 00:33:35.545
I promise that if I get to hold Donut,

00:33:37.065 --> 00:33:40.425
I won't come back to this house
or show my face again.

00:33:41.185 --> 00:33:42.665
Please, IngIng.

00:33:43.785 --> 00:33:44.785
Please.

00:33:46.705 --> 00:33:48.065
Please let me hold him.

00:33:57.585 --> 00:33:58.705
Donut.

00:33:58.785 --> 00:34:00.585
Wanna come to Daddy?

00:34:03.225 --> 00:34:04.345
Come to Daddy?

00:34:07.465 --> 00:34:08.465
Come on.

00:34:19.945 --> 00:34:20.945
Donut.

00:34:22.665 --> 00:34:23.784
Thank you.

00:34:28.065 --> 00:34:30.744
Shall we go downstairs and talk?

00:34:33.065 --> 00:34:34.344
Let's go together.

00:34:48.505 --> 00:34:49.545
Let's go.

00:34:53.784 --> 00:34:55.304
-Open the door!
-IngIng.

00:34:55.824 --> 00:34:57.905
If you still want to see your son,

00:34:58.425 --> 00:34:59.825
do as I say.

00:35:00.425 --> 00:35:02.385
Or I’ll sue you for custody
and take him back.

00:35:02.465 --> 00:35:04.425
-Open the door!
-IngIng.

00:35:04.505 --> 00:35:06.145
Open the door! Give me back my son!

00:35:06.225 --> 00:35:07.385
Open the door!

00:35:07.465 --> 00:35:08.305
Listen to me.

00:35:10.265 --> 00:35:12.425
Don’t tell anyone about this

00:35:13.105 --> 00:35:15.185
if you still want to see Donut.

00:35:15.705 --> 00:35:16.745
Do as I say.

00:35:16.825 --> 00:35:18.585
No! Open the door!

00:35:18.665 --> 00:35:20.905
Open the door! Give him back!

00:35:20.985 --> 00:35:23.105
Give me back my son!

00:35:23.185 --> 00:35:24.545
Open the door.

00:35:24.625 --> 00:35:26.225
I’ll take Donut with me,

00:35:27.065 --> 00:35:28.705
and you’ll never see him again.

00:35:29.465 --> 00:35:31.185
-No!
-Do as I tell you, IngIng.

00:35:31.265 --> 00:35:32.585
Donut!

00:35:34.505 --> 00:35:36.265
Don't do anything to him!

00:35:37.145 --> 00:35:38.385
Donut.

00:35:38.465 --> 00:35:40.345
Wait for me, okay?

00:35:40.425 --> 00:35:42.185
Just wait a little.

00:35:42.265 --> 00:35:44.025
I'll be right back.

00:35:53.905 --> 00:35:54.985
Ith.

00:35:55.065 --> 00:35:56.625
-Ith.
-Sis.

00:35:56.705 --> 00:35:57.785
-Ith.
-Ing.

00:35:59.465 --> 00:36:00.305
Where's Donut?

00:36:00.905 --> 00:36:02.825
Donut’s upstairs with Guy.

00:36:02.905 --> 00:36:05.065
How could you leave Donut with him?

00:36:05.145 --> 00:36:06.745
He threatened me.

00:36:06.825 --> 00:36:09.385
He said if I don’t do as he says,

00:36:09.465 --> 00:36:12.665
he'll sue me for full custody of Donut.

00:36:13.265 --> 00:36:14.465
That bastard.

00:36:15.065 --> 00:36:17.665
He told me not to tell anyone.

00:36:19.745 --> 00:36:21.545
What should I do?
I'm scared I'll lose Donut.

00:36:21.625 --> 00:36:22.985
What do we do, Ith?

00:36:25.545 --> 00:36:26.425
I'll help you.

00:36:31.065 --> 00:36:32.265
Come on.

00:36:45.625 --> 00:36:48.145
IngIng left all the messages on read.

00:36:48.225 --> 00:36:49.305
That's so strange.

00:36:49.385 --> 00:36:51.145
She's probably asleep.

00:36:54.265 --> 00:36:55.425
Where are you going, Ms. Lin?

00:36:55.505 --> 00:36:57.625
I'm going to check if something happened.

00:36:58.225 --> 00:36:59.225
Then I'll go with you.

00:36:59.305 --> 00:37:02.505
No need. Wait for me here,
so you can help if anything happens.

00:37:02.585 --> 00:37:04.945
Alright.
If you don’t call me in ten minutes,

00:37:05.025 --> 00:37:06.425
I'll call the police, okay?

00:37:33.185 --> 00:37:35.385
Oh? What brings you here?

00:37:35.905 --> 00:37:38.465
I was nearby for work,
so I thought I’d stop by.

00:37:38.545 --> 00:37:40.665
I called and texted you,

00:37:40.745 --> 00:37:42.225
but you didn’t respond at all.

00:37:43.585 --> 00:37:44.705
Oh.

00:37:45.345 --> 00:37:48.425
I must have been putting my son to sleep.

00:37:48.505 --> 00:37:49.705
I'm sorry.

00:37:54.585 --> 00:37:56.105
Is Donut upstairs?

00:37:56.705 --> 00:37:57.705
-Yes.
-Yes.

00:38:07.305 --> 00:38:08.185
You have a guest over?

00:38:08.265 --> 00:38:09.545
No.

00:38:10.225 --> 00:38:12.065
It's my friend,

00:38:12.145 --> 00:38:12.985
sleeping upstairs.

00:38:16.105 --> 00:38:17.145
Oh.

00:38:18.585 --> 00:38:19.985
Then I won't disturb you.

00:38:20.065 --> 00:38:22.025
See you at Play Park tomorrow.

00:38:22.105 --> 00:38:23.145
Yes.

00:38:23.665 --> 00:38:25.065
Drive home safely.

00:38:52.585 --> 00:38:54.265
Did you see IngIng's ex-husband?

00:38:54.345 --> 00:38:55.345
I didn't.

00:38:57.705 --> 00:38:58.745
But I feel something’s off.

00:38:58.825 --> 00:39:00.665
It’s like the two of them
were hiding something.

00:39:00.745 --> 00:39:03.265
She’s definitely hiding
her husband upstairs.

00:39:03.345 --> 00:39:05.545
It must be like I suspected, Ms. Lin.

00:39:05.625 --> 00:39:07.585
IngIng still hasn't divorced her husband,

00:39:07.665 --> 00:39:09.425
and now they're teaming up to scam you.

00:39:10.025 --> 00:39:11.785
She hasn't asked me for a single baht.

00:39:11.865 --> 00:39:14.425
We even split the dinner bills.
How could she be scamming me?

00:39:15.025 --> 00:39:18.585
Ms. Lin, this is the stage
where she gains your trust.

00:39:19.745 --> 00:39:21.385
Should we stay and watch?

00:39:22.025 --> 00:39:23.585
I remember her husband's face.

00:39:23.665 --> 00:39:25.425
We’ll find out the truth.

00:39:25.505 --> 00:39:26.585
Let's go.

00:39:26.665 --> 00:39:27.785
I'm exhausted.

00:39:28.865 --> 00:39:30.065
Ms. Lin…

00:39:30.145 --> 00:39:31.985
You’re afraid of the truth, aren’t you?

00:39:32.065 --> 00:39:32.945
I'm not.

00:39:33.945 --> 00:39:36.345
Then please go home. I’ll stay and watch.

00:39:50.865 --> 00:39:51.985
Donut.

00:39:52.545 --> 00:39:53.865
Come to Mama.

00:39:55.265 --> 00:39:56.225
Donut.

00:39:56.305 --> 00:39:57.705
Come to Mama, okay?

00:39:59.705 --> 00:40:00.865
How’s it going?

00:40:02.305 --> 00:40:03.505
What?

00:40:04.625 --> 00:40:06.465
Afraid he'll get
too attached to his father?

00:40:07.065 --> 00:40:08.585
Say what you came to say.

00:40:08.665 --> 00:40:09.625
Ms. Lin has left.

00:40:10.145 --> 00:40:11.265
Say it so you can leave too.

00:40:11.345 --> 00:40:13.465
In the divorce settlement,

00:40:13.985 --> 00:40:16.265
I granted you custody.

00:40:17.225 --> 00:40:18.945
But I’m not prohibited from visiting him.

00:40:19.705 --> 00:40:21.505
I was stupid to overlook that.

00:40:23.865 --> 00:40:25.865
Ing paid you to divorce her

00:40:25.945 --> 00:40:27.585
using almost all our money.

00:40:28.105 --> 00:40:29.865
Wasn’t that enough?

00:40:36.065 --> 00:40:37.425
How much more do you want?

00:40:43.265 --> 00:40:45.985
I'll agree to sign
an additional settlement

00:40:46.505 --> 00:40:48.905
never to see my son again

00:40:49.505 --> 00:40:52.545
and never let him know
that I’m his father.

00:40:53.225 --> 00:40:54.265
Is that okay?

00:40:58.745 --> 00:40:59.705
How much?

00:41:00.305 --> 00:41:01.145
Ing.

00:41:01.665 --> 00:41:03.905
Haven’t we paid him enough already?

00:41:05.865 --> 00:41:07.105
Take Donut upstairs.

00:41:10.425 --> 00:41:11.425
Let's go.

00:41:11.505 --> 00:41:12.825
Go with Uncle Ith.

00:41:13.345 --> 00:41:14.225
Go.

00:41:26.025 --> 00:41:27.465
You’re so quick to pay me, huh?

00:41:28.425 --> 00:41:30.105
Your new girlfriend must be rich.

00:41:30.705 --> 00:41:31.785
Ms. Lin has nothing to do with this.

00:41:32.305 --> 00:41:33.825
I’ll get the money myself.

00:41:34.905 --> 00:41:35.985
How much do you want?

00:42:12.305 --> 00:42:13.665
I'm her ex-husband.

00:42:13.745 --> 00:42:15.945
Are you crazy?
My boss has never been married.

00:42:16.025 --> 00:42:17.745
Is IngIng your boss?

00:42:18.465 --> 00:42:19.425
Hey.

00:42:21.385 --> 00:42:22.625
It's really him.

00:42:35.225 --> 00:42:36.545
Five hundred thousand?

00:42:37.825 --> 00:42:39.865
All our accounts combined
won’t even cover that.

00:42:41.025 --> 00:42:42.905
Where are you supposed to find
that kind of money?

00:42:43.505 --> 00:42:45.225
He said he'll give me a month.

00:42:45.305 --> 00:42:46.585
That's not enough time.

00:42:47.625 --> 00:42:49.505
Worst case, I’ll sell the car.

00:42:49.585 --> 00:42:50.745
Ing.

00:42:51.825 --> 00:42:54.185
It’s worth it if it ends this.

00:42:54.705 --> 00:42:56.585
And how much can we trust him?

00:42:59.465 --> 00:43:01.625
If he doesn’t sign, we don’t pay him.

00:43:01.705 --> 00:43:02.825
That’s fair, right?

00:43:04.225 --> 00:43:05.265
Should we tell Ms. Lin?

00:43:05.345 --> 00:43:06.465
No.

00:43:07.505 --> 00:43:09.225
Five hundred thousand
is just pocket change to her.

00:43:09.905 --> 00:43:11.825
Don't ever let Ms. Lin
find out about this.

00:43:18.985 --> 00:43:20.705
This is our family matter.

00:43:22.065 --> 00:43:23.465
I can handle it.

00:43:40.385 --> 00:43:42.145
It’s him. I’m certain.

00:43:42.225 --> 00:43:44.705
I remember IngIng's ex-husband clearly.

00:43:45.265 --> 00:43:47.025
They must be working together.

00:43:47.105 --> 00:43:49.025
You’re being scammed, Ms. Lin.

00:43:57.025 --> 00:43:59.665
IngIng seems so busy with work
that she hasn’t had time to see me.

00:43:59.745 --> 00:44:01.785
Do you have an urgent need for money?

00:44:01.865 --> 00:44:03.385
Ms. Lin, you have to stay firm.

00:44:03.465 --> 00:44:05.705
The evidence couldn't be clearer.

00:44:05.785 --> 00:44:07.225
They're tricking you.

00:44:07.305 --> 00:44:09.545
Since I started dating Ing,

00:44:09.625 --> 00:44:11.385
it’s felt like a dream, Jane.

00:44:11.465 --> 00:44:13.545
I've been really happy.

00:44:13.625 --> 00:44:15.225
How could a baby
just disappear like that, Ith?

00:44:15.305 --> 00:44:16.305
Or…

00:44:16.385 --> 00:44:18.345
could Donut have been kidnapped?

00:44:18.425 --> 00:44:20.465
Did you order Play Park
to be shut down, Dad?

00:44:20.545 --> 00:44:23.425
You shouldn’t have interfered
with my responsibilities.

00:44:23.505 --> 00:44:25.265
I feel betrayed.

00:46:22.225 --> 00:46:26.945
Subtitle translation by: Anan Pratchayakul